title: Soft
lyrics:
Paroles de la chanson Soft par Vacations
Right from the start
You take it to heart
Something so small
Stands so tall above you

Don't run
They're not so tough
Stand your ground
You're not so soft

You're looking too hard
For something that isn't there
Pull yourself out
You're overthinking what this is about

So don't run

They're not so tough
Stand your ground
You're not so soft
